Class ElasticsearchParserBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.yudyang.regulus.core.antlr4.ElasticsearchParserBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElasticsearchParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class ElasticsearchParserBaseListener
extends Object
implements ElasticsearchParserListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of ElasticsearchParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
